rows.label: campfev11_320_175_msg0001
rows.name:
Your Majesty...
About your intention to search for
the boy...

rows.label: campfev11_320_175_msg0003
rows.name:
Alst is presently mired in disorder,
and it is the work of the Grail's might.

rows.label: campfev11_320_175_msg0004
rows.name:
Nothing can right the balance but the
work of another Grail, alike in power.

rows.label: campfev11_320_175_msg0005
rows.name:
It pains me to say, but perhaps it is a
challenge too great for our nation to
face alone.

rows.label: campfev11_320_175_msg0006
rows.name:
So it's really in the Superbian national
interest if we act together on this.

rows.label: campfev11_320_175_msg0009
rows.name:
We'll take point on this one, Wadatsumi.
To ease the burden on His Majesty a
bit.

rows.label: campfev11_320_175_msg0011
rows.name:
Well then! I suppose we should look
lively and make our way out to
Seigle Fell.
